```plantuml
@startuml mcuking_offline-package-webpack-plugin

actor Developer
participant "OfflinePackagePlugin" as Plugin
participant "Webpack Compiler" as Compiler
participant "JSZip" as JSZip
participant "mime-types" as MimeTypes

Developer -> Plugin: Configure Plugin Options
Plugin -> Compiler: Apply Plugin

activate Compiler
Compiler -> Plugin: Emit Hook
activate Plugin

Plugin -> Plugin: Filter Files
alt File is included
    Plugin -> JSZip: Add File to Zip
end

Plugin -> MimeTypes: Detect MIME Type
Plugin -> Plugin: Generate index.json Manifest

Plugin -> Compiler: Emit Files
activate JSZip
JSZip -> Compiler: Zip Archive
deactivate JSZip

deactivate Plugin
deactivate Compiler
@enduml
```